author: @lycheeluiz3358
text:
omg hold on
in the music video, they’re dressed up as certain characters
i have a theory that each of the characters died in Knock Knock, but not only because they couldn’t get inside the house, it’s kinda dumb but it is still connected.
Nayeon committed suicide:
Nayeon’s character is a devil/demon, and it’s only seen in the mirror. Maybe when Nayeon looks at herself in the mirror, she sees her demons inside her (sort of) so obviously it’s kind of like, depression.
Jeongyeon is possessed by a ghost:
Pinnochio is Jeongyeon’s character, which is a puppet (duh). This shows that she is being forced to do something, maybe kill the other girls, then the ghost would kill Jeongyeon herself.
Momo died from starvation:
I’m not completely sure of Momo, but she’s Tinkerbell, who can fly. I do know Tinkerbell dies from lack of attention, maybe Momo wasn’t giving attention to certain parts of her own body, basically the stomach, and died.
Sana is the only one who lived:
Sana being batgirl(?) and the only character seen OUTSIDE of the mansion (idk about chaeyoung and Tzuyu’s in a kind of indoor garden) it is possible that she’s the only one who lived and possibly avenging the other eight or seven girls.
Jihyo died of freezing:
Jihyo is Elsa, who obv has some kind of freezing power, so maybe she was the first to die, in Knock Knock. 
Mina died from a gun or some kind of long-distance weapon:
Mina is a pirate, obv known for long-distance weapons like cannons, guns, harpoons so it’s obvious that she was killed by a long-distance weapon.
Dahyun died from a height:
Dahyun is a bunny rabbit, who tend to jump and leap and stuff, maybe she fell or jumped or maybe even was pushed, to a height that even a rabbit couldn’t jump off?
Chaeyoung was drowned:
yk, cos she was ariel and ariel is a mermaid, who spends a lot of time around water.
Tzuyu died from poisoning:
Maleficent is Tzuyu’s character (which I didn’t notice until I watched a few other videos on TT) and Maleficent has like a thing with poisoned apples, thus Tzuyu is in a greenhouse of sorts with apples on them.
